{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775870179497,"sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1c78a7001LokfCSPF8YSr2A","messageID":"msg_d7a1c7165001ZnCoH95jjt3649","sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870181248,"sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1c7afa001FqEp7NYyhv1db2","messageID":"msg_d7a1c7165001ZnCoH95jjt3649","sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_bf476828edde4f34bfeb9f8a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 创建处理器，将 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 的 HTTP 请求转化为 Kubernetes Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR 资源的创建操作。本变更是 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）的下游实现，覆盖请求验证、CR 构建、dynamic client 创建、状态等待（watcher 机制）、Pod IP 解析、Store 状态同步、失败回滚、CodeInterpreter Warm Pool 及 Auth 模式处理。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: SandboxCreateHandler 结构体与依赖注入\n10: \n11: The system SHALL define `SandboxCreateHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于创建 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、typed clientset（用于读取 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 模板）、informer factory（用于 informer cache 读取）、Store 接口（用于会话状态持久化）、SandboxReconciler watcher 接口（用于一次性状态等待）、token cache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、以及可选的 user client 工厂（EnableAuth 时使用）。\n12: \n13: #### Scenario: Handler 构造\n14: - **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、typed clientset、informer factory、Store、watcher 接口）均已初始化\n15: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxCreateHandler(deps)` 被调用\n16: - **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxCreateHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\n17: \n18: #### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\n19: - **GIVEN** token cache 或 user client 工厂为 nil（EnableAuth=false 场景）\n20: - **WHEN** Handler 构造完成\n21: - **THEN** 不 panic，相关字段为 nil，后续代码路径在 EnableAuth=false 时不访问这些字段\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ### Requirement: GVR 常量定义\n26: \n27: The system SHALL 定义以下 `schema.GroupVersionResource` 常量：`AgentRuntimeGVR`（group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1`, resource `agentruntimes`）、`CodeInterpreterGVR`（group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1`, resource `codeinterpreters`）、`SandboxGVR`（group `agents.x-k8s.io`, version `v1alpha1`, resource `sandboxes`）、`SandboxClaimGVR`（group `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io`, version `v1alpha1`, resource `sandboxclaims`）。\n28: \n29: #### Scenario: GVR 常量值正确\n30: - **GIVEN** 代码引用 `SandboxGVR`\n31: - **WHEN** 读取其 Group/Version/Resource 字段\n32: - **THEN** Group 为 `agents.x-k8s.io`，Version 为 `v1alpha1`，Resource 为 `sandboxes`\n33: \n34: #### Scenario: SandboxClaim GVR 值正确\n35: - **GIVEN** 代码引用 `SandboxClaimGVR`\n36: - **WHEN** 读取其 Group/Version/Resource 字段\n37: - **THEN** Group 为 `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io`，Version 为 `v1alpha1`，Resource 为 `sandboxclaims`\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ### Requirement: CreateSandboxRequest 请求模型与验证\n42: \n43: The system SHALL 定义 `CreateSandboxRequest` 结构体，包含字段 `Kind`（string）、`Name`（string）、`Namespace`（string），并提供 `Validate()` 方法。`Validate()` SHALL 拒绝 `Kind` 不为 `AgentRuntime` 或 `CodeInterpreter`、`Namespace` 为空、或 `Name` 为空的请求。Handler SHALL 从路由上下文覆写 `Kind` 字段（由端点路径决定，不信任请求体中的 Kind）。\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: 合法请求通过验证\n46: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"my-runtime\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n47: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n48: - **THEN** 返回 nil（无错误）\n49: \n50: #### Scenario: 空 namespace 被拒绝\n51: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"my-runtime\", Namespace: \"\"}`\n52: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n53: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 `namespace is required`\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: 空 name 被拒绝\n56: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Name: \"\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n57: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n58: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 `name is required`\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: 非法 Kind 被拒绝\n61: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxRequest{Kind: \"UnknownKind\", Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"}`\n62: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n63: - **THEN** 返回错误，错误信息包含 Kind 不为合法值\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: Handler 覆写 Kind\n66: - **GIVEN** 请求体 JSON 中 `kind` 字段为 `\"CodeInterpreter\"`，但请求发送到 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 端点\n67: - **WHEN** Handler 解析请求体并设置 `sandboxReq.Kind`\n68: - **THEN** `sandboxReq.Kind` 被覆写为 `\"AgentRuntime\"`（由端点决定，不信任请求体）\n69: \n70: ---\n71: \n72: ### Requirement: CreateSandboxResponse 响应模型\n73: \n74: The system SHALL 定义 `CreateSandboxResponse` 结构体，包含字段 `SessionID`（string, UUID）、`SandboxID`（string, CR 的 UID）、`SandboxName`（string, 格式 `{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`）、`EntryPoints`（`[]EntryPoint`，每个包含 `Path`、`Protocol`、`Endpoint`）。\n75: \n76: #### Scenario: 响应模型序列化\n77: - **GIVEN** `CreateSandboxResponse{SessionID: \"uuid-1\", SandboxID: \"uid-1\", SandboxName: \"my-runtime-abc12345\", EntryPoints: [{Path: \"/\", Protocol: \"HTTP\", Endpoint: \"10.0.0.1:8080\"}]}`\n78: - **WHEN** 序列化为 JSON\n79: - **THEN** JSON 包含 `sessionId`、`sandboxId`、`sandboxName`、`entryPoints` 字段，且值正确\n80: \n81: ---\n82: \n83: ### Requirement: POST /v1/agent-runtime — AgentRuntime Sandbox 创建流程\n84: \n85: The system SHALL 实现 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 端点的 handler，执行以下流程：\n86: 1. 解析请求体为 `CreateSandboxRequest`，校验 JSON 格式\n87: 2. 调用 `Validate()` 校验必填字段\n88: 3. 从 informer cache 读取 AgentRuntime 模板（按 Name + Namespace），若不存在返回 404\n89: 4. 验证模板 `spec.podTemplate` 不为 nil，否则返回 400\n90: 5. 生成 SessionID（UUID v4）和 SandboxName（`{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`）\n91: 6. 构建 Sandbox CR：APIVersion `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`，Kind `Sandbox`\n92: 7. 设置 labels：`app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: agentcube-workload-manager`、`runtime.agentcube.io/session-id`、`runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name`、`runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name`\n93: 8. 设置 annotations：`runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout`\n94: 9. 设置 lifecycle：`ShutdownTime = now + TTL`（TTL 取自 `MaxSessionDuration` 或默认 8h）\n95: 10. 设置 `Replicas: ptr.To[int32](1)`\n96: 11. Ports 从 `spec.Ports` 映射到 Sandbox spec\n97: 12. 调用 `StoreSandbox` 写入占位 SandboxInfo（sessionID → sandbox 元数据）\n98: 13. 注册一次性 watcher（`WatchSandboxOnce`）\n99: 14. 通过 dynamic client 创建 Sandbox CR\n100: 15. 等待 watcher 通知 Sandbox 状态变为 \"running\"（超时 2 分钟）\n101: 16. 解析 Pod IP\n102: 17. 调用 `UpdateSandbox` 更新 Store 中的完整信息\n103: 18. 构建并返回 `CreateSandboxResponse`（HTTP 200）\n104: \n105: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime Sandbox 创建成功\n106: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中存在名为 `my-runtime` 的 AgentRuntime，其 `spec.podTemplate` 非空，`spec.maxSessionDuration` 为 `8h`\n107: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 请求体 `{\"name\": \"my-runtime\", \"namespace\": \"default\"}`\n108: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 200，响应体包含 `sessionId`（UUID 格式）、`sandboxId`（CR UID）、`sandboxName`（格式 `my-runtime-XXXXXXXX`）、`entryPoints`（至少一个，endpoint 包含 pod IP 和端口）\n109: \n110: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 模板不存在\n111: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中不存在名为 `missing-runtime` 的 AgentRuntime\n112: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 请求体 `{\"name\": \"missing-runtime\", \"namespace\": \"default\"}`\n113: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404，响应体 `message` 指明 AgentRuntime 未找到\n114: \n115: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 缺少 podTemplate\n116: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中存在名为 `bad-runtime` 的 AgentRuntime，其 `spec.podTemplate` 为 nil\n117: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 请求体 `{\"name\": \"bad-runtime\", \"namespace\": \"default\"}`\n118: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400，响应体 `message` 指明 `podTemplate` 缺失\n119: \n120: #### Scenario: SandboxName 包含随机后缀\n121: - **GIVEN** workloadName 为 `my-runtime`\n122: - **WHEN** SandboxName 生成\n123: - **THEN** 格式为 `my-runtime-` 后接 8 位随机字母数字字符串\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR labels 正确\n126: - **GIVEN** 构建 Sandbox CR\n127: - **WHEN** CR 的 labels 被检查\n128: - **THEN** 包含 `app.kubernetes.io/managed-by: agentcube-workload-manager`、`runtime.agentcube.io/session-id`（值为 SessionID）、`runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name`（值为 workloadName）、`runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name`（值为 SandboxName）\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR annotations 包含 idle-timeout\n131: - **GIVEN** 构建 Sandbox CR\n132: - **WHEN** CR 的 annotations 被检查\n133: - **THEN** 包含 `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout`（值为配置的 idle timeout 字符串）\n134: \n135: #### Scenario: ShutdownTime 使用 MaxSessionDuration\n136: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 的 `spec.maxSessionDuration` 为 `4h`\n137: - **WHEN** Sandbox CR 的 lifecycle 被构建\n138: - **THEN** `ShutdownTime` 约为 `now + 4h`\n139: \n140: #### Scenario: ShutdownTime 使用默认值\n141: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 的 `spec.maxSessionDuration` 为 nil\n142: - **WHEN** Sandbox CR 的 lifecycle 被构建\n143: - **THEN** `ShutdownTime` 约为 `now + 8h`（默认值）\n144: \n145: #### Scenario: Replicas 设置为 1\n146: - **GIVEN** 构建 Sandbox CR\n147: - **WHEN** CR 的 spec.replicas 被检查\n148: - **THEN** 值为 `1`\n149: \n150: ---\n151: \n152: ### Requirement: POST /v1/code-interpreter — CodeInterpreter Sandbox 创建流程\n153: \n154: The system SHALL 实现 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 端点的 handler，流程与 AgentRuntime 类似，但有以下差异：\n155: - 从 informer cache 读取 CodeInterpreter 模板\n156: - 若 `WarmPoolSize > 0`：创建 SandboxClaim（而非完整 Sandbox），`sandboxEntry.Kind = SandboxClaimsKind`\n157: - 若 `WarmPoolSize == 0`：构建完整 Sandbox，容器名为 `code-interpreter`\n158: - 若 `AuthMode == picod`：从 `picod-router-identity` Secret 读取 public key，注入 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` 环境变量\n159: - 默认 ports：单个 `TargetPort{Port: 8080, Protocol: HTTP, PathPrefix: \"/\"}`\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Sandbox 创建成功（WarmPoolSize == 0）\n162: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中存在名为 `my-ci` 的 CodeInterpreter，`spec.warmPoolSize` 为 0 或 nil，`spec.template` 非空\n163: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 请求体 `{\"name\": \"my-ci\", \"namespace\": \"default\"}`\n164: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 200，创建的是完整 Sandbox CR（非 SandboxClaim），响应体包含 sessionId、sandboxId、sandboxName、entryPoints\n165: \n166: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Warm Pool 创建 SandboxClaim\n167: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中存在名为 `warm-ci` 的 CodeInterpreter，`spec.warmPoolSize` 为 `5`\n168: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 请求体 `{\"name\": \"warm-ci\", \"namespace\": \"default\"}`\n169: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 200，创建的是 SandboxClaim CR（APIVersion `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`，Kind `SandboxClaim`），响应体中 `sandboxEntry.Kind` 为 `SandboxClaimsKind`\n170: \n171: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter picod Auth 模式注入环境变量\n172: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 的 `spec.authMode` 为 `\"picod\"`，且 `picod-router-identity` Secret 中存在 public key\n173: - **WHEN** Sandbox CR 被构建\n174: - **THEN** 容器环境变量中包含 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`，值为 Secret 中的 public key\n175: \n176: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter picod Auth 模式 Secret 不存在\n177: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 的 `spec.authMode` 为 `\"picod\"`，但 `picod-router-identity` Secret 不存在\n178: - **WHEN** Handler 尝试读取 Secret\n179: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 401（或 500），错误信息指明 public key 缺失\n180: \n181: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 默认 ports\n182: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter 的 `spec.ports` 为空或 nil\n183: - **WHEN** Sandbox CR 被构建\n184: - **THEN** 使用默认 ports：`[{Port: 8080, Protocol: \"HTTP\", PathPrefix: \"/\"}]`\n185: \n186: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 缺少 template\n187: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中存在名为 `bad-ci` 的 CodeInterpreter，其 `spec.template` 为 nil\n188: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 请求体 `{\"name\": \"bad-ci\", \"namespace\": \"default\"}`\n189: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400，响应体指明 template 缺失\n190: \n191: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 模板不存在\n192: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中不存在名为 `missing-ci` 的 CodeInterpreter\n193: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 请求体 `{\"name\": \"missing-ci\", \"namespace\": \"default\"}`\n194: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404，响应体指明 CodeInterpreter 未找到\n195: \n196: ---\n197: \n198: ### Requirement: StoreSandbox 在 CR 创建前执行\n199: \n200: The system SHALL 在创建 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR 之前调用 `StoreSandbox`，写入占位 `SandboxInfo`（包含 sessionID、sandboxName、workloadName、namespace、Kind 等元数据）。若 `StoreSandbox` 失败，Sandbox 创建流程 SHALL 中止并返回 500。\n201: \n202: #### Scenario: StoreSandbox 先于 CR 创建\n203: - **GIVEN** 请求通过所有验证，准备创建 Sandbox\n204: - **WHEN** 创建流程执行\n205: - **THEN** `StoreSandbox` 在 dynamic client Create 之前被调用\n206: \n207: #### Scenario: StoreSandbox 失败中止创建\n208: - **GIVEN** Store 后端不可用（如 Redis 连接断开）\n209: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` 被调用\n210: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500，不创建 Sandbox CR\n211: \n212: ---\n213: \n214: ### Requirement: 一次性 Watcher 注册先于 CR 创建\n215: \n216: The system SHALL 在创建 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR 之前调用 `WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, sandboxName)` 注册一次性 watcher channel。该 watcher 用于接收 SandboxReconciler 发出的 \"running\" 状态通知。\n217: \n218: #### Scenario: Watcher 注册先于 Create\n219: - **GIVEN** StoreSandbox 成功完成\n220: - **WHEN** 创建流程继续\n221: - **THEN** `WatchSandboxOnce` 在 dynamic client Create 之前被调用\n222: \n223: #### Scenario: 同一 namespace/name 的 watcher 只注册一次\n224: - **GIVEN** 对同一 `namespace/sandboxName` 的并发创建请求\n225: - **WHEN** 两个请求同时到达\n226: - **THEN** watcher 机制保证每个 namespace/name 只有一个 watcher channel 被注册（或复用已有）\n227: \n228: ---\n229: \n230: ### Requirement: 等待 Sandbox 状态变为 \"running\"（2 分钟超时）\n231: \n232: The system SHALL 在创建 CR 后等待 watcher channel 通知 Sandbox 状态变为 \"running\"，超时时间为 2 分钟。若超时，Sandbox 创建流程 SHALL 返回错误 `sandbox creation timed out`，触发回滚机制。\n233: \n234: #### Scenario: Sandbox 在超时前进入 running\n235: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 已创建，SandboxReconciler 在 30 秒内将状态更新为 \"running\"\n236: - **WHEN** Handler 等待 watcher channel\n237: - **THEN** 在 30 秒内收到通知，流程继续到 Pod IP 解析\n238: \n239: #### Scenario: 等待超时\n240: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 已创建，但 SandboxReconciler 在 2 分钟内未将状态更新为 \"running\"\n241: - **WHEN** select 等待 watcher channel 超过 2 分钟\n242: - **THEN** 返回错误 `sandbox creation timed out`，触发回滚机制，HTTP 响应为 500\n243: \n244: ---\n245: \n246: ### Requirement: Pod IP 解析\n247: \n248: The system SHALL 按以下优先级解析 Pod IP：\n249: 1. 优先使用 sandbox name 作为 pod name\n250: 2. 若 Sandbox CR 的 annotation `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name` 存在，使用该值作为 pod name\n251: 3. 通过 informer cache 加载 Pod，要求 Pod 状态为 `Running` 且 `PodIP` 非空\n252: 4. 若按 name 未找到，使用 label selector `runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name=<sandboxName>` 查询 Pod，选择 owner reference 为 Kind `Sandbox` 且 name 匹配的 Pod\n253: \n254: #### Scenario: 使用 sandbox name 直接解析\n255: - **GIVEN** sandbox name 为 `my-runtime-abc12345`，存在同名 Pod 且状态为 Running，PodIP 为 `10.0.0.1`\n256: - **WHEN** Pod IP 解析执行\n257: - **THEN** 返回 `10.0.0.1`\n258: \n259: #### Scenario: 使用 annotation 回退解析\n260: - **GIVEN** sandbox name 对应的 Pod 不存在，但 Sandbox CR 的 annotation `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name` 值为 `actual-pod-name`\n261: - **WHEN** Pod IP 解析执行\n262: - **THEN** 使用 `actual-pod-name` 查找 Pod，返回其 PodIP\n263: \n264: #### Scenario: 使用 label selector 回退解析\n265: - **GIVEN** 按 name 和 annotation 均未找到 Pod\n266: - **WHEN** Pod IP 解析执行 label selector 查询\n267: - **THEN** 查询 label `runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name=my-runtime-abc12345`，选择 owner reference 为 Kind `Sandbox` 且 name 匹配的 Pod，返回其 PodIP\n268: \n269: #### Scenario: Pod 未 Running 时解析失败\n270: - **GIVEN** 找到的 Pod 状态为 `Pending`（非 Running）\n271: - **WHEN** Pod IP 解析执行\n272: - **THEN** 返回错误，指明 Pod 未处于 Running 状态\n273: \n274: #### Scenario: Pod 无 IP 时解析失败\n275: - **GIVEN** 找到的 Pod 状态为 Running 但 `PodIP` 为空\n276: - **WHEN** Pod IP 解析执行\n277: - **THEN** 返回错误，指明 Pod 无可用 IP\n278: \n279: ---\n280: \n281: ### Requirement: EntryPoint 构建\n282: \n283: The system SHALL 根据 resolved Pod IP 和 Sandbox 的 ports 配置构建 `EntryPoints`。每个 EntryPoint 的 `Endpoint` 为 `host:port` 格式（`host` 为 Pod IP，`port` 为配置的端口号），`Protocol` 取自 `TargetPort.Protocol`，`Path` 取自 `TargetPort.PathPrefix`。\n284: \n285: #### Scenario: 单端口 EntryPoint\n286: - **GIVEN** Pod IP 为 `10.0.0.1`，port 配置为 `[{Port: 8080, Protocol: \"HTTP\", PathPrefix: \"/\"}]`\n287: - **WHEN** EntryPoint 被构建\n288: - **THEN** 返回 `[{Path: \"/\", Protocol: \"HTTP\", Endpoint: \"10.0.0.1:8080\"}]`\n289: \n290: #### Scenario: 多端口 EntryPoints\n291: - **GIVEN** Pod IP 为 `10.0.0.1`，port 配置为 `[{Port: 8080, Protocol: \"HTTP\", PathPrefix: \"/\"}, {Port: 8443, Protocol: \"HTTPS\", PathPrefix: \"/api\"}]`\n292: - **WHEN** EntryPoint 被构建\n293: - **THEN** 返回两个 EntryPoints：`\"10.0.0.1:8080\"` 和 `\"10.0.0.1:8443\"`\n294: \n295: ---\n296: \n297: ### Requirement: UpdateSandbox 在 Pod IP 解析后执行\n298: \n299: The system SHALL 在 Pod IP 解析成功后调用 `UpdateSandbox`，将完整的 SandboxInfo（含 Pod IP、EntryPoints、SandboxID 等）写入 Store。若 `UpdateSandbox` 失败，Sandbox 创建流程 SHALL 记录错误但不回滚 CR（CR 已创建且 Sandbox 已 running）。\n300: \n301: #### Scenario: UpdateSandbox 成功\n302: - **GIVEN** Pod IP 解析成功，EntryPoints 已构建\n303: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox` 被调用\n304: - **THEN** Store 中该 sessionID 对应的 SandboxInfo 包含完整的 Pod IP 和 EntryPoints\n305: \n306: #### Scenario: UpdateSandbox 失败不回滚\n307: - **GIVEN** Pod IP 解析成功，但 Store 后端不可用\n308: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox` 被调用并返回错误\n309: - **THEN** 错误被记录，但已创建的 Sandbox CR 不被删除（Sandbox 已在 running 状态）\n310: \n311: ---\n312: \n313: ### Requirement: 失败回滚机制\n314: \n315: The system SHALL 在 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR 创建成功后，若后续步骤（状态等待、Pod IP 解析）失败，在 30 秒超时的 context 内删除已创建的 CR。回滚 SHALL 区分 Sandbox 和 SandboxClaim 类型，使用对应的 GVR 执行删除。若删除操作返回 `NotFound` 错误，视为成功（CR 已被其他组件删除）。\n316: \n317: #### Scenario: 状态等待超时触发回滚\n318: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 已成功创建，但 2 分钟内未进入 running 状态\n319: - **WHEN** 超时错误被捕获\n320: - **THEN** 在 30 秒超时 context 内调用 dynamic client Delete 删除 Sandbox CR，删除成功后返回原始超时错误\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: Pod IP 解析失败触发回滚\n323: - **GIVEN** Sandbox CR 已进入 running 状态，但 Pod IP 解析失败（Pod 未 Running）\n324: - **WHEN** 解析错误被捕获\n325: - **THEN** 在 30 秒超时 context 内删除 Sandbox CR\n326: \n327: #### Scenario: 回滚时 CR 已被删除\n328: - **GIVEN** 触发回滚时 Sandbox CR 已被 Garbage Collector 删除\n329: - **WHEN** dynamic client Delete 返回 `NotFound` 错误\n330: - **THEN** 视为回滚成功，不返回额外错误\n331: \n332: #### Scenario: SandboxClaim 回滚\n333: - **GIVEN** 创建的是 SandboxClaim（WarmPoolSize > 0 场景），后续步骤失败\n334: - **WHEN** 回滚机制触发\n335: - **THEN** 使用 `SandboxClaimGVR` 删除 SandboxClaim CR\n336: \n337: #### Scenario: 回滚超时\n338: - **GIVEN** 回滚删除操作在 30 秒内未完成\n339: - **WHEN** context 超时\n340: - **THEN** 删除操作被取消，错误被记录（CR 可能残留，需 Garbage Collector 后续清理）\n341: \n342: ---\n343: \n344: ### Requirement: 认证场景下的用户 Client 使用\n345: \n346: When `EnableAuth` is true, the system SHALL 使用基于用户 bearer token 构建的 per-user dynamic client 来创建/删除 Sandbox 或 SandboxClaim 资源。用户 client 的缓存 key 为 `<namespace>:<serviceAccountName>`。When `EnableAuth` is false, the system SHALL 使用 manager 的 in-cluster dynamic client。\n347: \n348: #### Scenario: EnableAuth=true 使用用户 client\n349: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth` 为 true，请求携带有效的 service account bearer token\n350: - **WHEN** Sandbox 创建流程执行 Create 操作\n351: - **THEN** 使用从 token 构建的 per-user dynamic client\n352: \n353: #### Scenario: EnableAuth=false 使用 manager client\n354: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth` 为 false\n355: - **WHEN** Sandbox 创建流程执行 Create 操作\n356: - **THEN** 使用 manager 的 in-cluster dynamic client\n357: \n358: #### Scenario: 用户 client 缓存命中\n359: - **GIVEN** 同一 namespace 和 service account name 的连续请求\n360: - **WHEN** `GetOrCreateUserK8sClient` 被调用\n361: - **THEN** 第二次请求命中缓存，不重新构建 client\n362: \n363: ---\n364: \n365: ### Requirement: 错误响应映射\n366: \n367: The system SHALL 将各类错误映射为统一的 HTTP 错误响应：\n368: - `400` — JSON 解析失败（`Invalid request body`）、请求验证失败（`required` 字段缺失）、模板缺失（`podTemplate is required` / `template is required`）\n369: - `404` — AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 模板在 informer cache 中不存在\n370: - `401` — EnableAuth 时 token 验证失败或 public key 缺失\n371: - `500` — 内部错误（Store 不可用、dynamic client 创建失败、超时 `sandbox creation timed out`、Pod IP 解析失败），响应体 `{\"message\": \"internal server error\"}` 或具体错误信息\n372: \n373: #### Scenario: 非法 JSON 请求体\n374: - **GIVEN** 请求体为非 JSON 内容（如纯文本 `hello`）\n375: - **WHEN** Handler 尝试绑定 JSON\n376: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400，响应体 `message` 为 `Invalid request body`\n377: \n378: #### Scenario: 验证失败 — namespace 为空\n379: - **GIVEN** 请求体 `{\"name\": \"test\", \"namespace\": \"\"}`\n380: - **WHEN** `Validate()` 被调用\n381: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400，响应体 `message` 包含 `namespace is required`\n382: \n383: #### Scenario: 模板不存在 — 404\n384: - **GIVEN** informer cache 中无匹配的 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter\n385: - **WHEN** Handler 尝试从 informer 获取模板\n386: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404，响应体 `message` 指明模板未找到\n387: \n388: #### Scenario: Store 不可用 — 500\n389: - **GIVEN** StoreSandbox 调用失败（Redis 连接断开）\n390: - **WHEN** 创建流程执行到 StoreSandbox 步骤\n391: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500，响应体 `message` 为 `internal server error`\n392: \n393: #### Scenario: 超时 — 500\n394: - **GIVEN** Sandbox 在 2 分钟内未进入 running 状态\n395: - **WHEN** 等待超时\n396: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500，响应体 `message` 为 `sandbox creation timed out`（或包含该信息的错误）\n397: \n398: ---\n399: \n400: ### Requirement: 统一 JSON 响应格式\n401: \n402: The system SHALL 使用 `pkg/workloadmanager/response` 包中的 `Created()` 和 `Error()`/`ErrorWithID()` 函数返回响应。成功创建返回 `200`（注意：sandbox-orchestration spec 定义为 200，非 201），响应体为 `CreateSandboxResponse` 的 JSON 序列化。错误返回使用统一的 `{\"message\": \"...\", \"code\": <int>}` 格式。\n403: \n404: #### Scenario: 成功响应格式\n405: - **GIVEN** Sandbox 创建成功\n406: - **WHEN** 响应被发送\n407: - **THEN** HTTP 状态码为 200，响应体包含 `sessionId`、`sandboxId`、`sandboxName`、`entryPoints`\n408: \n409: #### Scenario: 错误响应格式\n410: - **GIVEN** 创建流程中发生错误\n411: - **WHEN** 错误响应被发送\n412: - **THEN** 响应体为 `{\"message\": \"<error message>\", \"code\": <error code>}`，Content-Type 为 `application/json`\n413: \n414: ---\n415: \n416: ### Requirement: Sandbox 创建流程的端到端排序\n417: \n418: The system SHALL 严格按以下顺序执行 Sandbox 创建流程：\n419: 1. 请求解析与验证 → 2. 模板读取与校验 → 3. SessionID/SandboxName 生成 → 4. Sandbox CR 构建 → 5. StoreSandbox（占位）→ 6. WatchSandboxOnce 注册 → 7. Dynamic Client Create CR → 8. 等待 running（≤2min）→ 9. Pod IP 解析 → 10. UpdateSandbox → 11. 构建响应返回\n420: \n421: 任何步骤失败 SHALL 触发适当的错误响应，步骤 7 之后的失败 SHALL 触发回滚（删除已创建的 CR）。\n422: \n423: #### Scenario: 完整成功路径\n424: - **GIVEN** 所有依赖正常，AgentRuntime 模板合法，Store 可用，SandboxReconciler 正常工作\n425: - **WHEN** `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 被调用\n426: - **THEN** 以上 11 个步骤依次执行，最终返回 200 与完整响应\n427: \n428: #### Scenario: 步骤 2 失败（模板校验）不执行后续步骤\n429: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 模板的 `podTemplate` 为 nil\n430: - **WHEN** 创建流程执行到步骤 2\n431: - **THEN** 返回 400，不执行步骤 3-11，不创建任何 CR\n432: \n433: #### Scenario: 步骤 8 失败（超时）触发回滚\n434: - **GIVEN** 步骤 1-7 成功完成，但 SandboxReconciler 在 2 分钟内未将状态更新为 running\n435: - **WHEN** 步骤 8 超时\n436: - **THEN** 触发回滚（删除 CR），返回 500\n\n(End of file - total 436 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 创建处理器，将 `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 和 `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 的 HTTP 请求转化为 Kubernetes Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR 资源的创建操作。本变更是 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）的下游实现，覆盖请求验证、CR 构建、dynamic client 创建、状态等待（watcher 机制）、Pod IP 解析、Store 状态同步、失败回滚、CodeInterpreter Warm Pool 及 Auth 模式处理。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: SandboxCreateHandler 结构体与依赖注入\n\nThe system SHALL define `SandboxCreateHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于创建 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、typed clientset（用于读取 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 模板）、informer factory（用于 informer cache 读取）、Store 接口（用于会话状态持久化）、SandboxReconciler watcher 接口（用于一次性状态等待）、token cache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、以及可选的 user client 工厂（EnableAuth 时使用）。\n\n#### Scenario: Handler 构造\n- **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、typed clientset、informer factory、Store、watcher 接口）均已初始化\n- **WHEN** `NewSandboxCreateHandler(deps)` 被调用\n- **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxCreateHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\n\n#### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\n- **GIVEN** token cache 或 user client 工厂为 nil（EnableAuth=false 场景）\n- **WHEN** Handler 构造完成","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775870181240,"end":1775870181245}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870182616,"sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1c8051001RnleBglxjbuLhx","messageID":"msg_d7a1c7165001ZnCoH95jjt3649","sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5d579686ff9645a18df8f418","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-029: SDK HTTP 底层客户端 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `sdk-python`\n6: - **Language:** Python\n7: - **Size:** M\n8: - **Base specs:** `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: <!-- TODO: Add requirements in Given/When/Then format -->\n13: \n14: ## File Changes\n15: \n16: | Action | File | Description |\n17: |--------|------|-------------|\n18: | TODO | | |\n\n(End of file - total 18 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-029: SDK HTTP 底层客户端 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `sdk-python`\n- **Language:** Python\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n<!-- TODO: Add requirements in Given/When/Then format -->\n\n## File Changes\n\n| Action | File | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| TODO | | |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775870182609,"end":1775870182615}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775870182695,"sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1c8519001K4a9faKkzbKHAk","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7a1c7165001ZnCoH95jjt3649","sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":32050,"input":31871,"output":156,"reasoning":23,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.009091925}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775870186212,"sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1c92df001iFf0W34ta7BSLc","messageID":"msg_d7a1c8551001VW6oBa0SXjW305","sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870317176,"sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1ca38f0019Ji0XKvCVS8yO0","messageID":"msg_d7a1c8551001VW6oBa0SXjW305","sessionID":"ses_285e8b969ffeZ4XC0p6B2d0M7M","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_70847bf165644986b2e19add","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `manifests`\n- **Language:** YAML\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata\n\nThe chart SHALL define `Chart.yaml` with `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, and `appVersion: 1.0.0`.\n\n#### Scenario: Chart metadata fields are correct\n- **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` exists\n- **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\n- **THEN** `apiVersion` equals `v1`, `name` equals `agentcube`, `version` equals `0.1.0`, and `appVersion` equals `1.0.0`\n\n#### Scenario: Helm lint passes on chart metadata\n- **GIVEN** a valid `Chart.yaml` with the fields above\n- **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is run\n- **THEN** no errors or warnings related to chart metadata are reported\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: values.yaml default key tree\n\nThe chart SHALL provide a `values.yaml` with the full key tree documented in the deployment design, including typed defaults for `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis.addr`, `redis.password`, `router` (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rbac), `workloadmanager` (replicas, image, service, resources, extraEnv), and `volcano.scheduler` (enabled, replicas, image). Comments SHALL state that Redis settings must be provided by the user during installation.\n\n#### Scenario: Default values are valid YAML\n- **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml`\n- **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\n- **THEN** no parse errors occur and all top-level keys (`imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis`, `router`, `workloadmanager`, `volcano`) are present\n\n#### Scenario: Redis defaults are empty strings with comments\n- **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n- **WHEN** `redis.addr` and `redis.password` are read\n- **THEN** both default to `\"\"` and comments indicate they must be provided at install time\n\n#### Scenario: Router defaults match design\n- **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n- **WHEN** router values are read\n- **THEN** `router.replicas` is `1`, `router.image.repository` is `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router`, `router.image.pullPolicy` is `IfNotPresent`, `router.image.tag` is `latest`, `router.service.type` is `ClusterIP`, `router.service.port` is `8080`, `router.service.targetPort` is `8080`, resource limits are `cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi`, requests are `cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi`, `router.rbac.create` is `false`\n\n#### Scenario: Workload Manager defaults match design\n- **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n- **WHEN** workloadmanager values are read\n- **THEN** `workloadmanager.replicas` is `1`, `workloadmanager.image.repository` is `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager`, `workloadmanager.image.pullPolicy` is `IfNotPresent`, `workloadmanager.image.tag` is `latest`, `workloadmanager.service.type` is `ClusterIP`, `workloadmanager.service.port` is `8080`, resource limits are `cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi`, requests are `cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi`\n\n#### Scenario: Volcano scheduler defaults to disabled\n- **GIVEN** `values.yaml` is rendered\n- **WHEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled` is read\n- **THEN** it defaults to `false`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Workload Manager Deployment template\n\nThe template `workloadmanager.yaml` SHALL render a `Deployment` named `workloadmanager` in `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` with: replicas from `workloadmanager.replicas`; container `workloadmanager` using `repository:tag` with `imagePullPolicy`; port `http` on `workloadmanager.service.port`; env vars `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (fieldRef `metadata.namespace`), `REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, plus `workloadmanager.extraEnv`; args `--port=<port>` and `--runtime-class-name=` (empty); resource requests/limits from values; liveness probe HTTP GET `/health` (initialDelay 10s, period 10s); readiness probe HTTP GET `/health` (initialDelay 5s, period 5s); optional `imagePullSecrets`; `serviceAccountName: workloadmanager`.\n\n#### Scenario: Default deployment renders correctly\n- **GIVEN** default values and release namespace `agentcube`\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n- **THEN** the output contains a `Deployment` named `workloadmanager` in namespace `agentcube` with `replicas: 1`, container image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest`, and `imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent`\n\n#### Scenario: Health probes are configured\n- **GIVEN** default values\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Workload Manager container has liveness probe `httpGet /health` on the service port with `initialDelaySeconds: 10, periodSeconds: 10` and readiness probe `httpGet /health` with `initialDelaySeconds: 5, periodSeconds: 5`\n\n#### Scenario: Redis env vars are injected\n- **GIVEN** `--set redis.addr=redis.default.svc:6379 --set redis.password=secret123`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Workload Manager container env includes `REDIS_ADDR=redis.default.svc:6379` and `REDIS_PASSWORD=secret123`\n\n#### Scenario: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE uses fieldRef\n- **GIVEN** any valid installation\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Workload Manager container env includes `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` with `valueFrom.fieldRef.fieldPath: metadata.namespace`\n\n#### Scenario: extraEnv entries are appended\n- **GIVEN** `--set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"CUSTOM_VAR\",\"value\":\"custom-val\"}]'`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Workload Manager container env includes `CUSTOM_VAR=custom-val` in addition to the standard env vars\n\n#### Scenario: Container args include port and runtime-class-name\n- **GIVEN** `workloadmanager.service.port` is `8080`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the container args include `--port=8080` and `--runtime-class-name=`\n\n#### Scenario: Resource requests and limits from values\n- **GIVEN** default values\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the container resources have `requests: {cpu: 100m, memory: 128Mi}` and `limits: {cpu: 500m, memory: 512Mi}`\n\n#### Scenario: Custom replica count\n- **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.replicas=3`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Deployment spec has `replicas: 3`\n\n#### Scenario: Custom image override\n- **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.image.repository=myregistry/workloadmanager --set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.2.3`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the container image is `myregistry/workloadmanager:v1.2.3`\n\n#### Scenario: imagePullSecrets are applied when set\n- **GIVEN** `--set-json 'imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\":\"my-secret\"}]'`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Deployment `spec.template.spec.imagePullSecrets` includes `{name: my-secret}`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Workload Manager Service template\n\nThe template `workloadmanager.yaml` SHALL render a `Service` named `workloadmanager` in `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` with: `type` from `workloadmanager.service.type`; `port` and `targetPort` from `workloadmanager.service.port`; selector `app: workloadmanager`.\n\n#### Scenario: Default service renders\n- **GIVEN** default values\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** a `Service` named `workloadmanager` exists with `type: ClusterIP`, `port: 8080`, `targetPort: 8080`, and selector `app: workloadmanager`\n\n#### Scenario: Custom service type\n- **GIVEN** `--set workloadmanager.service.type=NodePort`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Service `type` is `NodePort`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Router Deployment template\n\nThe template `agentcube-router.yaml` SHALL render a `Deployment` named `agentcube-router` in `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` with: replicas from `router.replicas`; conditional `serviceAccountName` if `router.serviceAccountName` is non-empty; container `agentcube-router` using `router.image`; container port `router.service.targetPort`; env vars `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (fieldRef), `REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ workloadmanager.service.port }}`, plus `router.extraEnv`; args `--port=<targetPort>` and `--debug`; resources from values; liveness probe `/health/live` and readiness probe `/health/ready` on targetPort (initialDelay 1s, period 2s); optional `imagePullSecrets`.\n\n#### Scenario: Default router deployment renders\n- **GIVEN** default values and release namespace `agentcube`\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n- **THEN** the output contains a `Deployment` named `agentcube-router` in namespace `agentcube` with `replicas: 1` and image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router:latest`\n\n#### Scenario: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL resolves via in-cluster DNS\n- **GIVEN** release namespace `agentcube` and `workloadmanager.service.port` is `8080`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Router container env includes `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://workloadmanager.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080`\n\n#### Scenario: Router health probes\n- **GIVEN** default values\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Router container has liveness probe `httpGet /health/live` with `initialDelaySeconds: 1, periodSeconds: 2` and readiness probe `httpGet /health/ready` with `initialDelaySeconds: 1, periodSeconds: 2`\n\n#### Scenario: Router args include port and debug flag\n- **GIVEN** `router.service.targetPort` is `8080`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the container args include `--port=8080` and `--debug`\n\n#### Scenario: Conditional serviceAccountName\n- **GIVEN** `--set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Router Deployment `spec.template.spec.serviceAccountName` is `agentcube-router`\n\n#### Scenario: Empty serviceAccountName omits field\n- **GIVEN** `router.serviceAccountName` is `\"\"` (default)\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Router Deployment does NOT set `serviceAccountName`\n\n#### Scenario: Router extraEnv entries\n- **GIVEN** `--set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"LOG_LEVEL\",\"value\":\"debug\"}]'`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Router container env includes `LOG_LEVEL=debug`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Router Service template\n\nThe template `agentcube-router.yaml` SHALL render a `Service` named `agentcube-router` with: `type` from `router.service.type`; `port` from `router.service.port`; `targetPort` from `router.service.targetPort`; selector `app: agentcube-router`.\n\n#### Scenario: Default router service renders\n- **GIVEN** default values\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** a `Service` named `agentcube-router` exists with `type: ClusterIP`, `port: 8080`, `targetPort: 8080`, and selector `app: agentcube-router`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Workload Manager RBAC template\n\nThe template `rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` SHALL always render: a `ServiceAccount` named `workloadmanager` in the release namespace; a `ClusterRole` named `workloadmanager` with rules for agent-sandbox CRDs (`agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxtemplates`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools`, `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools/status`), AgentCube CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters`, `codeinterpreters/status`, `codeinterpreters/finalizers`, `agentruntimes`, `agentruntimes/status`), core resources (`pods`, `secrets`), and auth (`authentication.k8s.io/tokenreviews`); a `ClusterRoleBinding` named `workloadmanager` binding the ClusterRole to the ServiceAccount in the release namespace.\n\n#### Scenario: ServiceAccount renders in release namespace\n- **GIVEN** release namespace `agentcube`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** a `ServiceAccount` named `workloadmanager` exists in namespace `agentcube`\n\n#### Scenario: ClusterRole grants sandbox CRD permissions\n- **GIVEN** any valid installation\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the `ClusterRole/workloadmanager` includes rules granting `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` on `sandboxes` in `agents.x-k8s.io`\n\n#### Scenario: ClusterRole grants AgentCube CRD permissions\n- **GIVEN** any valid installation\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the `ClusterRole/workloadmanager` includes rules granting `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` on `codeinterpreters` in `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` and `get,list,watch` on `agentruntimes` in `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n\n#### Scenario: ClusterRole grants status and finalizer permissions\n- **GIVEN** any valid installation\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the ClusterRole includes `get,update,patch` on `codeinterpreters/status`, `update` on `codeinterpreters/finalizers`, and `update,patch` on `agentruntimes/status`\n\n#### Scenario: ClusterRole grants secrets and tokenreview permissions\n- **GIVEN** any valid installation\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the ClusterRole includes full verbs on `secrets` in core API group and `create` on `tokenreviews` in `authentication.k8s.io`\n\n#### Scenario: ClusterRoleBinding ties SA to ClusterRole\n- **GIVEN** release namespace `agentcube`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** `ClusterRoleBinding/workloadmanager` has subject `ServiceAccount/workloadmanager` in namespace `agentcube` and roleRef `ClusterRole/workloadmanager`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Optional Router RBAC template\n\nThe template `rbac-router.yaml` SHALL render **only if** `router.rbac.create` is true. When rendered, it SHALL create: a `ServiceAccount` named `{{ router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}` in the release namespace; a `Role` with the same name granting full verbs (`get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`) on `secrets` in the release namespace; a `RoleBinding` binding the Role to the ServiceAccount.\n\n#### Scenario: Router RBAC off by default\n- **GIVEN** `router.rbac.create: false` (default)\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n- **THEN** no Router ServiceAccount, Role, or RoleBinding resources appear in the output\n\n#### Scenario: Router RBAC enabled\n- **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the output contains a `ServiceAccount`, `Role`, and `RoleBinding` for the Router, all named `agentcube-router` (default)\n\n#### Scenario: Router RBAC with custom serviceAccountName\n- **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=my-router-sa`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the ServiceAccount, Role, and RoleBinding are all named `my-router-sa`\n\n#### Scenario: Router Role grants secret management\n- **GIVEN** `--set router.rbac.create=true`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Router Role includes rule: apiGroup `\"\"`, resources `secrets`, verbs `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Optional Volcano agent scheduler template\n\nThe template `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` SHALL render **only if** `volcano.scheduler.enabled` is true. When rendered, it SHALL create (in order): `ServiceAccount/volcano-agent-scheduler`; `ConfigMap/volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap` with key `agent-scheduler.conf` (actions `allocate`, tiers with predicates and nodeorder); `ClusterRole/volcano-agent-scheduler` with the full rule set from the deployment design; `ClusterRoleBinding/volcano-agent-scheduler-role`; `Service/volcano-agent-scheduler-service` (port 8080, metrics annotations); `Deployment/volcano-agent-scheduler` with replicas from `volcano.scheduler.replicas`, image from `volcano.scheduler.image`, args including `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler`, security contexts, and volumes for config + emptyDir.\n\n#### Scenario: Volcano scheduler disabled by default\n- **GIVEN** `volcano.scheduler.enabled: false` (default)\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is run\n- **THEN** no Volcano scheduler resources appear in the output\n\n#### Scenario: Volcano scheduler enabled\n- **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the output contains ServiceAccount, ConfigMap, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding, Service, and Deployment for the Volcano scheduler\n\n#### Scenario: Volcano ConfigMap contains scheduler config\n- **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** `ConfigMap/volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap` has key `agent-scheduler.conf` containing actions `allocate` and tiers with `predicates` and `nodeorder`\n\n#### Scenario: Volcano Deployment uses values for replicas and image\n- **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set volcano.scheduler.replicas=2 --set volcano.scheduler.image.tag=v1.0.0`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Volcano Deployment has `replicas: 2` and image `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler:v1.0.0`\n\n#### Scenario: Volcano Deployment args include scheduler name\n- **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Volcano container args include `--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler`\n\n#### Scenario: Volcano Service has metrics annotations\n- **GIVEN** `--set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** `Service/volcano-agent-scheduler-service` has port `8080` and Prometheus metrics annotations\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: CRDs shipped with chart\n\nThe chart SHALL ship `CustomResourceDefinition` manifests under `crds/` directory: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` and `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`. Both SHALL use API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1` (served and storage), and `scope: Namespaced`.\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntime CRD is present\n- **GIVEN** the chart directory `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds` is run\n- **THEN** the output contains `CustomResourceDefinition/agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` with `spec.group: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, `spec.versions` including `v1alpha1` as served and storage, and `scope: Namespaced`\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreter CRD is present\n- **GIVEN** the chart directory `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base --include-crds` is run\n- **THEN** the output contains `CustomResourceDefinition/codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` with `spec.group: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, `spec.versions` including `v1alpha1` as served and storage, and `scope: Namespaced`\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntime CRD required spec fields\n- **GIVEN** the AgentRuntime CRD YAML\n- **WHEN** its `openAPIV3Schema` is inspected\n- **THEN** `spec.required` includes `maxSessionDuration`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, and `targetPort`\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreter CRD required spec fields\n- **GIVEN** the CodeInterpreter CRD YAML\n- **WHEN** its `openAPIV3Schema` is inspected\n- **THEN** `spec.required` includes `template` and `spec.authMode` defaults to `picod`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Helm install command with required values\n\nThe chart SHALL support installation via `helm upgrade --install <release> manifests/charts/base --namespace <ns> --create-namespace` with `--set redis.addr=...` and optional `--set redis.password=...`. All component workloads SHALL render without manual editing of the output YAML.\n\n#### Scenario: Install with minimal required values\n- **GIVEN** a Kubernetes cluster with Helm 3\n- **WHEN** `helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube --create-namespace --set redis.addr=redis.agentcube.svc:6379 --set redis.password=pass --wait` succeeds\n- **THEN** Deployments `workloadmanager` and `agentcube-router`, Services, RBAC, and CRDs are all created in namespace `agentcube`\n\n#### Scenario: Install with component image overrides\n- **GIVEN** local images loaded into a Kind cluster\n- **WHEN** `helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base --namespace agentcube --create-namespace --set redis.addr=redis.agentcube.svc:6379 --set redis.password=\"\" --set workloadmanager.image.repository=workloadmanager --set workloadmanager.image.tag=latest --set router.image.repository=agentcube-router --set router.image.tag=latest --wait` succeeds\n- **THEN** Workload Manager and Router Deployments use the local image names and tags\n\n#### Scenario: Install with router RBAC and extraEnv\n- **GIVEN** a cluster with Helm 3\n- **WHEN** install includes `--set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router --set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED\",\"value\":\"false\"}]'`\n- **THEN** Router RBAC resources are created and Router pods have the specified extraEnv\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Helm upgrade preserves state\n\nThe chart SHALL support upgrading an existing release with modified values without deleting existing resources (except where Helm's native upgrade semantics dictate replacement).\n\n#### Scenario: Upgrade replica count\n- **GIVEN** a release installed with default values (1 replica for Workload Manager)\n- **WHEN** `helm upgrade` is run with `--set workloadmanager.replicas=3`\n- **THEN** the Workload Manager Deployment is updated to `replicas: 3` without downtime (rolling update)\n\n#### Scenario: Upgrade image tag\n- **GIVEN** a release installed with `workloadmanager.image.tag=latest`\n- **WHEN** `helm upgrade` is run with `--set workloadmanager.image.tag=v1.1.0`\n- **THEN** the Workload Manager Deployment image is updated to `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:v1.1.0`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Helm template dry-run produces valid Kubernetes manifests\n\nThe chart SHALL produce valid Kubernetes YAML when rendered with `helm template`, with no unresolved template variables and all required fields populated from defaults or overrides.\n\n#### Scenario: Default template output is valid\n- **GIVEN** default values\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is piped to `kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -`\n- **THEN** no validation errors are reported\n\n#### Scenario: Template with all overrides is valid\n- **GIVEN** `--set redis.addr=redis.ns.svc:6379 --set redis.password=secret --set volcano.scheduler.enabled=true --set router.rbac.create=true`\n- **WHEN** `helm template test manifests/charts/base` is piped to `kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -`\n- **THEN** no validation errors are reported\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Namespace scoping via Release.Namespace\n\nAll namespaced resources SHALL use `{{ .Release.Namespace }}` for their namespace field, not hardcoded values.\n\n#### Scenario: Workload Manager Deployment uses release namespace\n- **GIVEN** `--namespace production`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Workload Manager Deployment has `metadata.namespace: production`\n\n#### Scenario: Router Service uses release namespace\n- **GIVEN** `--namespace staging`\n- **WHEN` templates are rendered\n- **THEN** the Router Service has `metadata.namespace: staging`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: nameOverride and fullnameOverride support\n\nThe chart SHALL support `nameOverride` and `fullnameOverride` values for customizing resource names, following Helm naming conventions.\n\n#### Scenario: Default naming convention\n- **GIVEN** default values and release name `my-release`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** resource names follow the chart's default naming (e.g., `workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router`)\n\n#### Scenario: fullnameOverride renames resources\n- **GIVEN** `--set fullnameOverride=agentcube-prod`\n- **WHEN** templates are rendered\n- **THEN** applicable resource names use `agentcube-prod` as the base name\n\n## File Changes\n\n| Action | File | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` | Chart metadata (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0, appVersion 1.0.0) |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` | Default configuration values for all components (Redis, Router, Workload Manager, Volcano) |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml` | Workload Manager Deployment + Service with health probes, Redis env vars, extraEnv |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml` | Router Deployment + Service with health probes, WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL, conditional serviceAccountName |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | Workload Manager ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Optional Router ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding (gated by router.rbac.create) |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Optional Volcano scheduler resources (gated by volcano.scheduler.enabled) |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` | AgentRuntime CRD (group runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh, v1alpha1, Namespaced) |\n| Create | `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` | CodeInterpreter CRD (group runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh, v1alpha1, Namespaced) |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775870317153,"end":1775870317173}}}}
